    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚当局加强选举调查，突击搜查布拉索夫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/romanian-authorities-step-up-election-probe-with-brasov-raids</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚最高法院取消了亲俄新贵与亲欧候选人之间的总统决选，罗马尼亚检察官在对涉嫌选举违规行为进行调查的第二天突击搜查了多处房产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/romanian-authorities-step-up-election-probe-with-brasov-raids</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 12:00:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹永哲在戒严令失败后幸免于弹劾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/south-korea-impeachment-vote-drags-on-after-ruling-party-boycott</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈周六在弹劾投票中幸存下来，因为他的执政党拒绝加入反对派的罢免行动，此前他短暂宣布戒严，震惊全国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/south-korea-impeachment-vote-drags-on-after-ruling-party-boycott</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 10:46:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国议员否决调查第一夫人的法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/south-korean-lawmakers-reject-bill-to-investigate-first-lady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在韩国国会试图弹劾其丈夫、总统尹锡烈之前，国会气氛紧张，但韩国议会以微弱优势未能通过对第一夫人股票交易进行调查的议案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/south-korean-lawmakers-reject-bill-to-investigate-first-lady</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 09:54:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爆炸造成多人受伤，海牙公寓受损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-07/urgent-an-explosion-has-caused-several-injuries-and-damaged-apartments-in-the-dutch-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰海牙（美联社）——据当局称，周六凌晨，荷兰海牙市一处街区发生爆炸和火灾，造成多套公寓被毁，多人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-07/urgent-an-explosion-has-caused-several-injuries-and-damaged-apartments-in-the-dutch-capital</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 09:50:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尹永哲弹劾动议聚焦韩国代沟问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/yoon-s-impeachment-sharpens-focus-on-korea-s-generational-gap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈的弹劾投票凸显了代沟的扩大。一边是支持尹锡烈的年长保守派选民。另一边是更年轻、更自由的韩国人，他们指责总统及其政治盟友缺乏就业机会，阻碍了他们的进步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/yoon-s-impeachment-sharpens-focus-on-korea-s-generational-gap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 09:47:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴黎圣母院向马克龙和其他世界领导人重新开放大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-07/notre-dame-reopens-its-doors-to-macron-and-other-world-leaders-in-a-rare-symbol-of-unity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴黎（美联社）——法国标志性建筑巴黎圣母院将于周六正式重新开放，这是自 2019 年一场毁灭性的大火几乎摧毁这座拥有 861 年历史的地标建筑以来的首次重新开放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-07/notre-dame-reopens-its-doors-to-macron-and-other-world-leaders-in-a-rare-symbol-of-unity</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 07:02:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳选举总统，重点关注债务和生活成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/ghana-election-what-mahamudu-bawumia-and-john-mahama-are-promising</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三十多年来，加纳的政治权力一直在两个政党之间轮换。周六的选举后，这种情况几乎肯定会继续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/ghana-election-what-mahamudu-bawumia-and-john-mahama-are-promising</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>提前重置竞标失败后，斯塔默触发工党警报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/keir-starmer-already-faces-labour-unrest-after-attempted-reset-falls-flat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 发表了旨在重启英国首相生涯的重要演讲，但演讲失败。工党上下纷纷呼吁他采取更大胆的政策和更犀利的讯息，以重新与选民建立联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-07/keir-starmer-already-faces-labour-unrest-after-attempted-reset-falls-flat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
